now create some new files in this repo

* touch amazon aws 

track now and do commit also
after done commit do push the code

* git push origin main(branch-name)     -----------------> command to push the code from git/local to github/central


Now lets create some branches and do push into github/central

* git checkout -b newbranchname         -----------------> command to create a new branch and switch to the new branch as well
now we will do some files commit

* touch google netflix

track these files do push

* git add *                       -----------------> command to track files
* git commit -m "new files" .     -----------------> command to commit files . means hidden files also
